# Vocal Media Post – Day 01

## Title:
How Digital Companions Are Transforming Web3 Virtual Worlds

## Summary:
In today’s Vocal Media post, I explore how digital companions like Bubus are reshaping virtual worlds in Web3. The article explains how intelligent NFT characters enhance immersion, create emotional engagement, and introduce new interactive possibilities inside decentralized ecosystems.

